Examples :

  $ export ENCODING_TO=ISO-8859-1
  $ ./utfopo da.po

will convert da.po to ISO-8859-1 for editing.


  $ ./potoutf da.po

will convert da.po to UTF-8 for use with gtk+ 1.3.

The charset= line will be changed as appropriate, as long
as it is of the right format.


These scripts are public domain and UNDER NO WARRANTY.

Backup your .po files before entrusting them to my script.

[Addendum: these scripts are obsoleted by msgconv from
 gettext 0.11.]
